ZH: 我的外婆现在住在养老院。
EN: My grandmother now lives in a nursing home.

ZH: 这家养老院提供了很好的护理服务。
EN: This nursing home provides excellent care services.

ZH: 养老院里的老人们都很快乐。
EN: The elderly people in the nursing home are all very happy.

ZH: 我们的城市建了一家新的养老院。
EN: Our city has built a new nursing home.

ZH: 这个养老院有专门的医疗团队。
EN: This nursing home has a dedicated medical team.

ZH: 我们对养老院做了一次参观。
EN: We took a tour of the nursing home.

ZH: 这个养老院有很多康复设施。
EN: This nursing home has many rehabilitation facilities.

ZH: 我的父母计划在退休后住进养老院。
EN: My parents plan to move into a nursing home after retirement.

ZH: 养老院里有一个大花园，老人们可以在那里散步。
EN: There is a large garden in the nursing home where the elderly can take walks.

ZH: 养老院每周都会组织一些娱乐活动。
EN: The nursing home organizes entertainment activities every week.

ZH: 这家养老院提供24小时的护理服务。
EN: This nursing home provides 24-hour care services.

ZH: 养老院的员工非常亲切和体贴。
EN: The staff at the nursing home are very kind and considerate.

ZH: 我的祖父在养老院里认识了很多朋友。
EN: My grandfather has made many friends in the nursing home.

ZH: 这个养老院有一个舒适的休息室供老人们放松。
EN: This nursing home has a cozy lounge for the elderly to relax.

ZH: 养老院提供优质的食物和饮料。
EN: The nursing home provides high-quality food and drinks.

