EN: This nursing home is built in a peaceful rural area.

ZH: 我们筹备了一个义卖会来支持养老院。
EN: We organized a charity sale to support the nursing home.

ZH: 这个养老院有很好的安全措施，保障老人们的安全。
EN: This nursing home has good security measures to ensure the safety of the elderly.

ZH: 我们定期去探望在养老院里的亲人和朋友。
